<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About Us | MedTrack</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #f4f9fd;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #0077cc;
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    header img {
      height: 40px;
      margin-right: 1rem;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .about-section {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .about-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #0077cc;
    }

    .about-section p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .team-section {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .team-section h3 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #0077cc;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .team-cards {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .team-card {
      background-color: #f9fcff;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      width: 200px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .team-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .team-card img {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .team-card h4 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .team-card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      background-color: #e0e0e0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      header {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
      nav {
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1><img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/ffffff/health-book.png" alt="Logo"> MedTrack</h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a> 
      <a href="#team">Team</a>
      <a href="/contactus">Contact</a>
      <a href="/login">Login</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="about-section" id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
      Welcome to <strong>MedTrack</strong>, your trusted partner in managing healthcare efficiently. 
      Our platform is designed to streamline the connection between patients, doctors, and administrators 
      by providing a centralized system to manage appointments, diagnoses, and medical history.
    </p>
    <p>
      At MedTrack, we believe in empowering users with intuitive tools and secure access to critical 
      health information. Whether you are a patient booking appointments, a doctor tracking diagnoses, 
      or an admin managing operations, MedTrack simplifies your workflow.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our mission is to make healthcare accessible, organized, and data-driven. With a focus on 
      innovation, privacy, and user-friendliness, MedTrack aims to be the backbone of modern digital 
      healthcare systems.
    </p>
  </main>

  <section class="team-section" id="team">
    <h3>Meet the Team</h3>
    <div class="team-cards">
      <div class="team-card">
        <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg" alt="John Doe">
        <h4>John Doe</h4>
        <p>Lead Developer</p>
      </div>
      <div class="team-card">
        <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/44.jpg" alt="Jane Smith">
        <h4>Jane Smith</h4>
        <p>UI/UX Designer</p>
      </div>
      <div class="team-card">
        <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/76.jpg" alt="Sam Patel">
        <h4>Sam Patel</h4>
        <p>Database Architect</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 MedTrack. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
